high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Go to the right side of the sink.
Cut the lettuce inside the sink.
Turn around the go to the refrigerator.
Place the knife inside the refrigerator on the second shelf from the top.
Turn around the go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink.
Go to the stove on the left.
Put the cut lettuce inside the square pan on the back of the stove.
Pick up the pan and the lettuce in it.
Turn around to go back to the refrigerator.
Place the pot and the lettuce on the top shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put lettuce in a pan into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink.
Grab the knife from the leftmost sink.
Head to the rightmost sink.
Slice up the fruit that is in the sink.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Place the knife in the second row of the fridge.
Turn right back to the sinks.
Grab a slice of the fruit.
Turn right to the stove.
Place the fruit slice on the back right pan.
Grab the pan that has the fruit in it.
Turn around back to the fridge.
Place the pan in the top row of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife and a slice of fruit on a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Take the knife with the yellow handle from the lower edge of the sink.
Turn right and take one step, then turn left to face the sink on the right.
Use the knife to cut the lettuce in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge and then close the door.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Place the lettuce in the pan at the back of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the lettuce in it.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and take one step, then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the pan inside.
